Sin City: A Dame Fatal is based on three stories from Frank Miller and has elements of Just Another Saturday Night (Just Another Saturday Night), plus two new stories, one titled The Long Bad Night. Inside the gloomy Sin City, Dwight (Josh Brolin) is sought by the only woman he ever loved, Ava Lord (Eva Green), while Nancy (Jessica Alba) tries to cope with the death of Hartigan (Bruce Willis). The plot takes place before The Big Fat Kill (present in Sin City - Sin City) and explains how Dwight came to have a dramatically different face.
